Turkish Court Rules Against Health Ministry, Hurriyet Reports

-- B y   S t e v e   B r y a n t
-- 
2011-04-08T05:07:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-08/turkish-court-rules-against-health-ministry-hurriyet-reports.html
Turkey ’s top administrative court
cancelled a Health Ministry decision stopping doctors at state
hospitals from also operating private clinics, Hurriyet
newspaper reported.  The ministry plans to appeal against the Ankara court’s
decision, the newspaper said, citing Health Minister Recep
Akdag.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
